50:00.196 --> 50:05.293
Um, just wanted to remind you
I go on at 10:00 tonight.

50:05.334 --> 50:07.894
I... I promise not to suck.

50:07.937 --> 50:10.497
No pressure.

50:10.540 --> 50:12.974
