I can see that.

53:13.756 --> 53:16.850
I don't know why exactly.

53:16.892 --> 53:19.156
You didn't want to get sued.

53:19.195 --> 53:21.220
Right?

53:24.300 --> 53:27.133
Oh.

53:27.169 --> 53:30.366
- Hi.
- Hi.

53:34.644 --> 53:37.044
So I just had a little talk
with Rasheen.

53:38.514 --> 53:40.243
I asked about you being
his big brother.

53:40.282 --> 53:41.977
He had no idea
what I was talking about.

53:42.018 --> 53:44.145
Okay. Okay, wait.

53:44.186 --> 53:47.587
He said you met on the subway.
What the fuck is going on?

53:47.623 --> 53:49.215
Hold... hold... hold... hold on.
Hold on.

53:49.258 --> 53:51.283
- Just wait.
- Who is he? Why is he here?

53:51.327 --> 53:55.058
He got separated from his...
he had nowhere else to go.

53:55.097 --> 53:56.428
- How old is he?
- I don't know.

53:56.465 --> 53:59.263
- He doesn't know either.
- And...

53:59.301 --> 54:00.791
oh my God,
do you like little boys?

54:00.836 --> 54:03.896
What? No!
He's... he's in foster care, okay?

54:03.939 --> 54:05.873
He's been in seven
foster homes in his life.

54:05.908 --> 54:08.809
I... I think something was going on.
He says he won't go back.

54:08.844 --> 54:11.404
- Why didn't you go to the police?
- I did!

54:11.447 --> 54:13.608
Look, I... I realize
I'm in some trouble here,

54:13.649 --> 54:14.741
but I don't know what else to do.

54:14.784 --> 54:17.651
I'm just... I'm letting him stay here
until I can figure something out.

54:17.687 --> 54:21.145
- How long has he been here?
- Three, four days.

54:21.190 --> 54:25.684
You find a child on the subway
and you think you can just...

54:25.728 --> 54:28.162
just keep him here without letting
anyone know where he is?

54:28.197 --> 54:30.256
- That's...
- And you left him here

54:30.299 --> 54:31.789
while you were out
the other night.

54:31.834 --> 54:34.234
No, he was fine.
I... I put on some Leonard Cohen.

54:34.270 --> 54:36.261
He just knocked him right out.

54:38.741 --> 54:41.471
I have the worst taste in men.

54:49.452 --> 54:50.942
Sorry.

