like, first thing

01:02:21.303 --> 01:02:23.703
I didn't think I should
ever get married?

01:02:23.739 --> 01:02:26.264
- That I come from a long line...
- You come from a long line...

01:02:26.308 --> 01:02:28.139
- of divorced people.
- That's right.

01:02:28.177 --> 01:02:31.704
