Why now?

01:02:38.120 --> 01:02:39.781
Love.

01:02:41.190 --> 01:02:43.658
Huh.

01:02:43.692 --> 01:02:46.991
Wow.

01:02:47.029 --> 01:02:49.827
You really want out, don't you?

01:02:56.171 --> 01:03:01.905
