have to be red?!"

01:07:23.405 --> 01:07:26.465
- Yes! Go, Dad!
- Right? That was awesome.

01:07:26.508 --> 01:07:27.805
- That was awesome.
- Wow.

01:07:27.843 --> 01:07:29.242
And that was like a...
from that point on,

01:07:29.277 --> 01:07:31.108
