I will. It's...

01:11:38.326 --> 01:11:41.591
- Hi.
- Oh, hey.

01:11:41.629 --> 01:11:45.827
Um, Mississippi, Annie.
Annie, the famous Mississippi.

01:11:45.867 --> 01:11:48.836
- And I'm not famous?
- Shut up.

01:11:48.870 --> 01:11:51.566
- It's so nice to meet you.
